flowchart TB
  subgraph Modes[Operating modes]
    ProdNormal[PROD normal chat]
    ProdSlash[PROD temporary handoff action]
    DevStage[DEV stage chat]
    DevIntegration[DEV integration mode]
    ProdPromotion[PROD promotion mode]
  end

  subgraph Capabilities[Capability boundary]
    ReadProdContext[Read selected PROD context]
    EnqueueHandoff[Enqueue immutable handoff]
    EditStageFiles[Edit assigned stage worktree]
    RunStageTools[Run stage tests and agents]
    MergeDevMain[Integrate stage into dev/main]
    DrainProd[Drain active PROD jobs]
    RestartProd[Restart PROD backend]
    ReleaseApps[Release DEV and PROD APKs]
    ReadDevInternals[Read DEV internals]
    ExecuteAdHoc[Execute ad hoc shell or git commands]
  end

  ProdNormal --> ReadProdContext
  ProdNormal -. denied .-> EditStageFiles
  ProdNormal -. denied .-> ReadDevInternals
  ProdNormal -. denied .-> ExecuteAdHoc
  ProdNormal -. denied .-> RestartProd

  ProdSlash --> ReadProdContext
  ProdSlash --> EnqueueHandoff
  ProdSlash -. denied .-> EditStageFiles
  ProdSlash -. denied .-> RunStageTools
  ProdSlash -. denied .-> ExecuteAdHoc

  DevStage --> EditStageFiles
  DevStage --> RunStageTools
  DevStage -. denied .-> MergeDevMain
  DevStage -. denied .-> RestartProd

  DevIntegration --> MergeDevMain
  DevIntegration -. denied .-> RestartProd
  DevIntegration -. denied .-> ReleaseApps

  ProdPromotion --> DrainProd
  ProdPromotion --> RestartProd
  ProdPromotion --> ReleaseApps
  ProdPromotion -. denied .-> ExecuteAdHoc

